curl could parse mime type and decide where to push the stream, POC:<p><pre><code>    #!/usr/bin/env sh

    case $(curl -sLI $1 | grep -i content-type) in
        *text*) echo &quot;curl $1&quot;
                ;;
        *) echo &quot;curl $1 > $(basename $1)&quot;
           ;;
    esac
</code></pre>
